history.content:
Political Computer Science APPLICATIONS DUE TODAY by 11:59 PM PST!!! Our application should take no longer than 20 minutes so apply now!

Quick Application: https://forms.gle/UNJUkmkwJRyTjkLZA

PCS provides students interested in the intersection of technology and politics with a space to tap into both of these backgrounds. We are currently recruiting for both technical and non-technical roles! If you are interested in developing politically-centered tech projects aimed at addressing issues within political systems, PCS is the perfect place for you!  

Check out our linktree https://linktr.ee/pcsberkeley for the Spring 2021 application, a recording to the info session, and more information. Feel free to reach out via email (pcs.berkeley@gmail.com), Facebook, or Instagram (@pcs_berkeley) if you have any additional questions!
history.subject: Political Computer Science Applications due TONIGHT!
